kpi.name: M386B2C27

kpi_info.title: The average call setup time of the subscriber released connections
kpi_info.use: The average call setup time of the durations of the subscriber released connections during the period. Clear code range for internal failure released connection: C00...FFF. The unit of time in ASCII report is seconds, in XML reports it is 10 milliseconds.

kpi.kpi_alias: The average call setup time of the subscriber released connections
